"{\"correct\": \"no\", \"explanation\": \"The code incorrectly uses sns.lmplot() within the g.map() function. The lmplot() function is a figure-level function and cannot be used in the context of an axes-level function like map(). Instead, g.map() should be used with sns.regplot() or sns.scatterplot() for plotting on the FacetGrid.\", \"patch\": \"6c6,8\\n< g.map(sns.lmplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n---\\n> g.map(sns.regplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n> g.add_legend()\\n> \\n\"}"